title: #306 - Eddie Bravo
description:
Eddie Bravo, Owner of 10th Planet Jiu Jitsu , joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt live in studio.
 
The Fourth Eddie Bravo Invitational takes place August 15, 2015 at the Orpheum Theatre in Los Angeles, CA.
 
All info can be found here: http://www.eddiebravoinvitational.com/
